title: (PSX-PSP) Mortal Kombat Mythologies:Sub Zero converted properly
description:
MORTAL KOMBAT MYTHOLOGIES - SUB ZERO:

MK MYTHOLOGIES: Sub-Zero focuses on the popular MK character Sub-Zero, as it delves into his past with Scorpion, and how he got involved in the Mortal Kombat tournament. MKM plays like an MK game except that instead of fighting in the confines of an arena, you are free to run around the environment. The controls are identical to MK3, except that buttons for picking up items and turning around have been added. Sub-Zero's MK3 combos are available as are his special moves, which must be earned through experience points. You'll also get impressive FMV sequences that help tell the story and explain a lot of unanswered questions about Sub Zero's past.

Tested and working on all CFW's 5.00 m33 and above using the 500 popsloader pack set on 3.72 POPS...KloWn
